<paragraph blockId="1.[264,1325,780,1778]" pageId="1" pageNumber="32">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[264,507,780,806]" pageId="1" pageNumber="32">General characters</emphasis>
. Small sized (forewing length 
<quantity box="[884,989,780,806]" metricMagnitude="-3" metricUnit="m" metricValue="8.5" metricValueMax="9.0" metricValueMin="8.0" pageId="1" pageNumber="32" unit="mm" value="8.5" valueMax="9.0" valueMin="8.0">8–9 mm</quantity>
). Body yellowish or orange except for abdomen much darker. Wings grayish brown.
</paragraph>
